data.description: This beautiful 2 story home features  over 1800 sq. ft. finished + unfinished basement for your future expansion. Offering 3 beds, 3 baths, this home packs a lot of bang for the buck! Formal 2 story photo with upper level cat walk is perfect for photo ops. Foyer is flanked by two large rooms that could be dining/family/office/rec/flex...you decide. The huge Hearth room is the heart of the home with wood burning fireplace and opens to breakfast room. Centrally located powder room. Breakfast area has sliding doors out to paver patio and nice back yard. Kitchen has light cabinets, stainless appliances, HD counters and big pantry. MAIN FLOOR LAUNDRY just off 2 car garage. Upstairs the catwalk landing is open to below. Large master w/vaulted ceiling, large walk in closet and bath with deep garden tub and walk in shower.  Hall bath w/tub shower combo.  This home has been recently refreshed! Seller to give buyer a $5000 credit for an improvement of their choice!
